{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "暗火四起", "storyInfo": "風笛認識了正準備溜回軍營的簡，簡答應她尋找線索。號角見到上校，得知駐軍因塔拉人和鬼魂部隊的暴力襲擊而損失慘重。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，挨了好幾下砸，還是沒能追上凱利上尉。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，這塊手帕給你，好好擦擦，不然這些爛葉子會留味道的。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到除了凱利上尉，還有我們的士兵會自願到十七區來。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的士兵？這麼說，你也是嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，我是偷偷溜出來的。我不敢穿制服。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是穿了那身衣服，還想從這裡抄近路回軍營，會讓附近的居民不高興吧。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，是這樣嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難怪，我明明沒說什麼，也跟著挨了一通爛葉子爛水果轟炸。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是新調來的嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧，我是從倫蒂尼姆來的。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，倫蒂尼姆！我還沒去過呢。那裡一定比小丘郡大得多......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎片大廈真的有三百多層嗎？皇家科學院底下的山體裡是不是真的埋著傳送法陣，能通往奇跡空間，裡面有初代德拉克王的寶藏？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......啊？寶藏？我都沒聽說過哎。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我倒是知道高速陸地軍艦出廠時候是什麼樣子，也見過水培植物工作室......你要是想知道這方面的事情，我倒是可以告訴你哦。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍艦？水培工作室......？這好像......和小說裡的倫蒂尼姆不太一樣......啊！抱歉！還是別讓我打岔啦。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你想查案，就這麼到這條街上來，可能很難問出結果。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定還會像這樣......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像這樣平白多了一身臭味？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好哈哈，也沒那麼臭啦。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些居民和我們士兵的衝突經常發生嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前都是小摩擦，最近變得緊張了起來。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像你聽到的，連著出了好幾起針對我們士兵的襲擊案，大家的神經都很緊繃——", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道真是鬼魂部隊......奇怪，他們以前不怎麼針對普通士兵。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬼魂......你在說什麼呀？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒什麼。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，剛才那巡邏兵叫這裡的居民“塔拉渣滓”——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，別、別在這裡真的叫出來啊！他們又在瞪我們了......還是說你想收到更多爛蔬菜禮包？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......好的。他們真的不是維多利亞人？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們當然是維多利亞人。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我越來越糊塗了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些人會選擇另一個詞，是的，就是你聽到的那個——塔拉人，來指代他們的身份。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會這麼叫的人裡既有當地居民，也包括相當一部分士兵。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說的話，我也聽過這個詞。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在小說裡？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在歷史課本裡。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，他們一直在這裡。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早在好幾百年前，小丘郡還不是小丘郡，我們的移動城市還沒有建起來，放眼望去全是青草覆蓋的山谷的時候，這地方就是他們的家。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得那位德拉克蓋爾王的傳說......發源地是不是就在這一帶？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時這個地區就被稱作塔拉。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，關於蓋爾王的傳奇小說，我還看過很多本呢。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位蓋爾王，帶著當時的塔拉人，和初代阿斯蘭王之間有過一場戰爭，但幾年之後，就也隨著倫蒂尼姆的王一起簽訂了和平條約吧？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為，在那之後，塔拉這個詞語就不怎麼被提起了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在來小丘郡以前，我也這麼認為......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，維多利亞一直在變化，不是嗎？我們瓦伊凡也不是向來就生活在這裡，但我們現在都是維多利亞的國民。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是人人都這麼想的話，很多衝突就不會發生了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也用不著沮喪啦，我們之所以在這裡，不就是為了揪出真正的敵人，阻止更大的衝突嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你寧可頂著一頭爛菜葉也不肯走？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你是不是覺得我很傻？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，完全沒有。其實，我覺得你很厲害。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與剛才那位巡邏兵類似的粗暴言行，我見過很多。我不是沒想過阻止......可惜我只是一名儀仗兵。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儀仗兵怎麼了？你也是維多利亞軍隊的一員，你當然能夠改變眼下這個你自己不喜歡的局面！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......真、真的嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你......你是第一個這麼對我說話的人。嗯，下次我會試試看......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#3$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我還能幫到你什麼嗎？除了摘掉這幾片菜葉子......畢竟，我也不想看著衝突愈演愈烈。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想想......你有沒有認識的當地朋友？我想問一下達米安·巴里平時經常會去什麼地方。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "認識的朋友......西爾莎或許知道些什麼。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我個聯絡方式吧，我等一會去趟報社，我想今天士官長也不會介意我在不在......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G2_opera_room", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡曼德羅斯。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見過你的父親——二十多年前，在開斯特公爵舉辦的舞會上。當然，那時我還是個小小的衛兵，只遠遠看了一眼傳說中的白狼伯爵。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不久之後，我聽說他在倫蒂尼姆的猛獸園裡被一隻畸形的帶羽爬蟲嚇出了一場病，迅速離開了貴族社交圈。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從此再也沒有離開過位於港口城的自家莊園一步。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現下令尊還好嗎？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝您的關心，希望懷念這些陳年舊事沒有佔用太多您寶貴的時間。畢竟，想見您一面可算不上容易。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不像你的父親。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#4"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "顯然，家父並沒有機會如您和我一般為帝國軍隊效力。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "考慮到此次軍用源石製品失竊案不可能與他有關，我們或許可以不必繼續探討他的晚年生活了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個人的出身將決定他成為一個什麼樣的人。你同意這句話嗎，斯卡曼德羅斯？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認為人們有權利選擇自己的未來。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽聽，多麼符合你身份的答案。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯蘭的親信要族之後，皇家近衛學校的優等生，倫蒂尼姆的軍中新貴——你當然以為自己能改變任何事。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不想改變什麼，上校。您不必擔心我們小隊的到來會影響您在小丘郡的指揮權......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個笑話一點都不好笑。你不會自大到以為我會把一個小小的中尉放在眼裡吧？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像你這樣的人我見得多了。總是誇誇其談，捨本逐末。我願意見你，是想警告你——", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不懂的事情少插手。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#2"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我不能同意。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們收到的命令就是要查清失竊源石製品的下落。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你好好地在該待的地方待著，過不了多久，你就能完成你的任務，風風光光地回到倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說的風光，我不需要，維多利亞更不需要。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不習慣用未經審判就匆匆砍下來的人頭交差。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈！你在說我草菅人命——你以為那些人真是無辜的？多麼可笑！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在十天前，我們有三名士兵被殘忍地殺害。詹姆斯·科恩，羅伯特·鮑里斯，傑瑞米·布朗。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "科恩的妻子寫信告訴他自己懷上第二個孩子的時候，她還不知道她丈夫的腦袋上已經多了一個血肉模糊的洞。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鮑里斯下半年就能離開這個地方，他說退役之後要回去繼承家裡的布料生意。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有布朗，他一年前還是個聰敏的學生，死的時候甚至不到二十！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#5"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對他們的犧牲深表惋惜。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "惋惜！哈，多麼輕飄飄的辭令，就像從你嘴裡說出來的每一句話。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是為什麼我們都想抓住兇手。上校，在這件事上，我們的立場始終一致。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺害他們的人就是這群塔拉渣滓。我們已經揪出來了兩個，但我知道背後還藏著更多個。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十五天前，我們的軍營有三處同時遭到了爆炸物襲擊，十五名士兵犧牲。炸開的洞和我們人的血到現在都還在原地。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十一天前，我們的補給運輸隊在北郊物流區外遇到埋伏，一整支隊伍連同貨物全部不翼而飛。你覺得他們還有活著的可能嗎？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這還只是近一個月裡發生的事，你對我們長久以來承受的損失一無所知。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#2"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說的這些事件，聽起來都很像是鬼魂部隊所為。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在過去半年內，倫蒂尼姆陸陸續續收到了來自十餘個郡的報告，記錄了多達上百起的謀殺、搶劫、破壞案件。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們每次犯案之後都會很快隱匿行蹤，所有見過他們的相關人員都會在與我們接觸之前就遭到暗殺。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到目前為止我們能得到的情報還很少。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是為何眼前的線索至關重要。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還不知道鬼魂部隊在小丘郡出沒的目的，但我相信他們是我們共同的敵人。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上校，如果我們能和駐軍合作，在這裡揭開鬼魂部隊的真面目，這對小丘郡和維多利亞來說都大有裨益。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，你還是一點都不明白。你把眼前的慘劇當成一個能夠為你贏來又一枚獎章的案件。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#4"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你錯了，士兵，這不是案件，也不存在什麼真正的犯人。這是戰爭，是我們和他們之間，已經持續了幾十年、甚至上百年的戰爭。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你叫他們鬼魂部隊，可你知道這個名字意味著什麼？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你當我們一直以來面對的敵人是誰？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是鬼魂！是漂浮在這座城市上空、回蕩在愚蠢的塔拉人腦袋裡的，陰魂不散的幽靈！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#2"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個幽靈說著和我們不一樣的語言，歪曲著我們的祖先用雙手創造的歷史，妄想著有一天借著我們城市的軀殼還魂！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#2"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你是說當地居民裡有大量鬼魂部隊的支持者？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#4"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大量？支持者？不，你錯了。他們是一個整體。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#6"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看到這本詩集了嗎？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西莫·威廉姆斯，他的詩在倫蒂尼姆也有些名氣。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是他們編纂出來的關於維多利亞的謊話。在他們的描繪裡，他們有著自己的語言，是這片土地天生的主人。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞尚能包容來自不同文化背景的創作者的想法。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒人會把做夢的人說的夢話當真，除非他在夢中拿起了斧子，想要把我們的腦袋砍下來。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我留著這本癡人囈語，是為了讓上面的血跡時刻提醒我自己——", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果一個人生在維多利亞的土地上，卻不願意用維多利亞語通報自己的名字，那他就不再是維多利亞人，而是威脅著帝國安危的敵人！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你處決了這本詩集的持有者？就因為他......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才受到襲擊的第九防衛隊和第十三防衛隊和指揮中心徹底失聯。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第五、第七和第十防衛隊各自派了先鋒趕到現場，他們沒有發現敵人的蹤跡。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的人呢？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......全部犧牲。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽到了嗎，斯卡曼德羅斯？", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在你跟我說這些同情敵人的廢話的同時，我們又有一批優秀的士兵死在了他們手上！", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_227_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽懂了就請滾出我的辦公室，還有真正的工作等著我去做。", "name": "漢密爾頓上校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_227_1#1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，正好，我也有我的工作要做。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}